Purchase a movie ticket for John Wick Parabellum at any of the participating Cine Prestige cinemas for showtimes between Friday 17 May and Sunday 19 May. If a gold coin is found on your reserved Cine Prestige, take the coin to the promoter after the movie to redeem an instant prize.  In order to be entered into the promotion, entrants must follow this process:  Super-Assassin John Wick (Keanu Reeves) is on the run after killing a member of the international assassin’s guild, and with a $14 million price tag on his head – he is the target of hit men and women everywhere.  Director: Chad Stahelski Writers: Derek Kolstad and Shay Hatten Stars: Keanu Reeves, Halle Berry and Ian McShane     